Creating a service to monitor CPU Usage and send alerts.

Steps to implement:
1. Python Script 

2. locate in Python how to monitor the CPU Usage 
Psutil module - libary for retriving information on running Processes and system utilization 

3. Select how to notify Desktop notification using notification from Plyer module 

4. Creating the script 
• import the necessary libraries
- Psutil 
- time 
- Plyer.noticitation 
• Define necessary functions 
- Send notification 
- monitor CPU usage 
• Main Program execution 
- Get the alert threshold and the check interval as a input and not as a set Parameter. 

The Service would continuously monitor the CPU usage as often as set in the check-interval input
